features: 【HIGH-PERFORMANCE VOCAL MICROPHONE】With Wider Response Frequency and Higher Acceptable Sound Pressure Level, The On55 Dynamic Microphone Delivers Higher Quality Sound and More Sound Details, Perfect For Recording Studio and Singing Applications.

【GREAT OFF-AXIS REJECTION】ON55 singing microphone uses a cardioid Poly Pattern to ensure great Off-Axis Rejection, Reducing Noise From the Background and Capturing Source Sound. Besides The Bulid-in Pop-filter Plus Mesh Grille Protects The Mic Against Wind Interference and Singer's Split, Ensures Clearly Sound.

【SOLID and DURABLE】ON55 karaoke microphone Steel Mesh Grille and Metal Enclosure Protecting Microphone Against Scratch, Comfortable For Holding and Not Afraid Of Dropping. The Connection Of Cable Uses Tensile Design and Bulletproof Filler , Shielding The Cable From Bending.
【GOLD PLATED XLR to 1/4" CABLE】Ideal Audio Solution For Sending Balanced Audio to Ensure Minimal Signal Loss and Improve Signal Transmission.

【Package Content】Handheld Dynamic Vocal Microphone X 1, 16ft XLR Cable X 1, Microphone Clip X 1, User Manual X 1.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: OneOdio Wired Dynamic Microphone Engineered specifically to pair with the full line of speakers, the Oneodio ON55 delivers a sound experience like no other. Easy plug-n-play setup lets you instantly sing along to your favorite tunes.

Frequency response: 40 Hz - 15,000 Hz Professional Performance Level Sound The Oneodio ON55 Professional Dynamic Microphone provides reliable studio and stage-tested performance, with an ultra-wide frequency response range making it perfect for vocals, and the heart-shaped microphone mode minimizing background noise.

Unique Feature Bulletproof filler makes it last over 10,000 bends, with no static/noise or burst. Additional features include built-in acoustic pop-filter, high signal audio output, rugged construction with steel mesh grill, ON/OFF switch for stage control, along with an included 15' foot XLR connection cable.

We provide a microphone clip that makes it easy for you to match your microphone stand. Fully equipped with an effective windscreen and pop filter, performance is improved.An internal shockproof sponge reduces the noise transmitted through the solid during hand-held operations.

The 16.4t XLR audio cable makes sure of a tight connection as well as offers a clear, smooth-flowing optimal signal. Durable connectors and double shielding, provide optimal signal transfer and corrosion resistance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great microphone at a great price !!
reviews.reviewText: The microphone easily works with any sound amplifier. I am a music teacher, and I had been using the"stock" microphone that came with my portable amplifier. The stock microphone broke almost instantly. I had to order another, but being a teacher, I couldn't afford an expensive one. The OneOdio55 microphone works wonderfully. The sound is crisp and clear, and the microphone itself is very sturdy. The microphone clip can be used with a standard microphone stand. Great value for a great price !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: One Odio ON55 microphone. The price belies what you are getting. Incredible value.
reviews.reviewText: This mic looks and feels quality. I have compared it on my setup with a Shure SM 58, a Sennheiser 835S and a Behringer XM8500. For my voice, l prefer the sound of the ON55. I bought it when I saw it advertised because I had previously bought studio headphones from the same maker and was more than impressed. I use them in preference to others that I have that cost many times more. The ON55 did not disappoint. It's a great mic, amazing value and, as l said the price belies the quality you're getting. GET one and try it, you won't regret the spend.

Qualità del prodotto eccellente, uno dei migliori mai provati. Ovviamente non parliamo di microfoni da €500 ma di prodotti economici che hanno una resa professionale, ed è vero.Diciamo che il valore reale di questo prodotto se venisse commercializzato con un marchio noto potrebbe essere di circa €100.
